            "title_1": "How to Use",
            "icon_name_1": "",
            "raw_content_1": "<ol><li>Slide your aluminum tube through the prongs of the Tube Key, positioning it at the bottom of the tube.</li><li>Fold the Tube Key over to squeeze product toward the opening.</li><li>Continue folding the tube with the key as you use product, working your way up the tube.</li><li>When finished, unfold and remove the Tube Key before recycling your empty aluminum tube.</li></ol><p><em>For best results with Skin Emulsion, begin using the Tube Key when approximately 1/4 of the product remains to ensure you receive full value from your purchase.</em></p>",
