    "section_faq_4mrHcA": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "text_V3abL8": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "What is Skin Wash used for?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Skin Wash used for?",
            "content": "<p>Cleansing all skin, head-to-toe. Skin Wash is a foaming gel cleanser designed to replace your face wash, body wash, hand soap, makeup remover, and even shaving gel or bubble bath. One product, endless uses.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_w3ncCf": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it a facial cleanser or body wash?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it a facial cleanser or body wash?",
            "content": "<p>It’s both—and more. Skin Wash is formulated to be effective enough to remove makeup and SPF, yet gentle enough for sensitive skin anywhere on the body.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_gWBybL": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it safe for sensitive skin?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe for sensitive skin?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Skin Wash is made with mild, baby-safe surfactants and hydrating humectants. It’s passed clinical testing on sensitive skin, however, if you are sensitive to gentle fragrances, we recommend waiting for our fragrance-free Skin Wash in the future. ;)</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_8VE3Fe": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Does it remove makeup?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does it remove makeup?",
            "content": "<p>Yes! Skin Wash effectively removes sunscreen, light-to-medium makeup, and daily buildup without drying your skin. For waterproof mascara, we recommend using a dedicated makeup remover first.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_fArmLD": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Is it safe during pregnancy and for kids?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe during pregnancy and for kids?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, Skin Wash is safe for use during pregnancy and for the whole family. If using on young children or infants, we recommend checking with your pediatrician. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_ezhJbm": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "How long does a bottle last?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does a bottle last?",
            "content": "<p>That depends on how you use it. If using as a face wash only, it can last several months. With full-body use, it will last 1-2 months, so we recommend pairing with our refill pouch to reduce waste and restock with ease. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
